New features
--------------------

- I need load all plugins sql in config_shop.php
- I need define size images on admin.
- Rewriting users.
- Rewriting cart with a class.
- Rewriting products and properties. Now, a product can have different characteristics selectionables.
- New theme.
- Plugins are loading via hooks. A product can have hooks too. All elements have hooks, including prices.
- Support for loading products data via sockets, net or files.
- Support for extra fields on products table.
- Change to dompdf.
- Images on db.

